---
title: Lemon-Dill Roasted Salmon Serves 4 | with Avocado 'Hollandaise' Sauce
description: Nothing says treating mom like slow-roasted salmon, coated in fresh dill and zingy lemon zest. We've swapped out traditional Hollandaise with a luxurious avocado-lemon sauce for an elevated brunch feast!
